,{"type":"entry","text":"medium wave 中波","headword":"medium wave"},{"type":"entry","text":"short wave 短波","headword":"short wave"},{"type":"entry","text":"kilocycle [ˈkɪləsaɪkl]","headword":"kilocycle"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.千周，千赫"},{"type":"entry","text":"midnight [ˈmɪdnaɪt]","headword":"midnight"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.午夜，子夜"}]},{"number":1349,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"live broadcast 直播","headword":"live broadcast"},{"type":"entry","text":"be on the air 正在广播，正在播送","headword":"be on the air"},{"type":"entry","text":"magnetic [mæɡˈnetɪk]","headword":"magnetic"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.有磁性的，富有吸引力的，有魅力的"},{"type":"entry","text":"deep-voiced [ˌdiːp ˈvɔɪst]","headword":"deep-voiced"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.声音低沉的"},{"type":"entry","text":"husky [ˈhʌski]","headword":"husky"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.低沉沙哑的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎husky voice低沉沙哑的嗓音"},{"type":"entry","text":"recorded broadcast 录音后广播","headword":"recorded broadcast"},{"type":"entry","text":"transmitter [trænsˈmɪtə(r)]","headword":"transmitter"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.（电台信号的）发射机，发射台"},{"type":"entry","text":"indoor aerial 室内天线","headword":"indoor aerial"},{"type":"entry","text":"tape recorder 磁带录音机","headword":"tape recorder"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"}]},{"number":1350,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"A：Can you turn the radio off? I have such a headache.（你能把收音"},{"type":"text","text":"机关掉吗？我觉得头疼。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Sure, no problem.（当然，没问题。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Let me see. Hmm, she wears a pair of glasses.（让我看看。嗯，"},{"type":"text","text":"她戴着一副眼镜。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：OK. I have written it down, let's go to the supermarket, and we"},{"type":"text","text":"will have an emergency broadcast by the loudspeaker.（好的。我已经写"},{"type":"text","text":"下来了，我们去超市用喇叭紧急广播一下吧。）"}]}]}